| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2850 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 7b1afcfc-64ed-52c5-a38a-d0e9d36cae82"
